column4: ɔdze ahoɔdzen abɔ noho do: Wiadze so wɔdze etsim hɔ dɛ orinnhihim."

column2: "W’ahengua tsim hɔ fi tsetse: Ɔwo fi ɔdomankoma."

column5: Nsuyirii no ama hɔn ndze do
column6: Nsuyirii no ama hɔn asorɛkye do."

column2: "Ɔsor EWURADZE no yɛ tumfo Sen esu pii ne ndze
column3: Sen po asorɛkye a ɔwɔ tum mpo."

column2: "Wo mbrasɛm tsim hɔ ara pi: Krɔnkrɔnyɛ fata wo fie
